	   <tr><td colspan=2>hi im uandar a ranger on the saryrn server, a while back i gave up on my ranger and started a shaman, but then started to play my ranger more, and more and more to the point now where i dont play my shaman more. but i've been thinking of having an alt, and so im gonna start him up again, i only got my shaman up to lvl 9, and hes got some banded armor that my ranger got for him, and im soon gonna give him better because im upgrading my rangers equipment. but since i know next to nothing about shamans i would like to help. and if u dont mind i'm gonna ask a few questions.<br><br>1) What kind of armor should i be looking at, at lvl 10 to my 20s?<br><br>2) what weapon skill should i be focussing most on? blunt 1h, 2h, or peircing. at the moment im practicing both 1hb and peirce.<br><br>3) What weapons should i get? i have at the moment a cracked staff, and a rusty shortened spear.<br><br>4) Are there any nice little quests i could do for any armor?<br><br>5) Where is a good place for a shaman to use his/her skills to the biggest extent possible to get the most out of it?<br><br>6) And finally can someone give me a little summary about shamans? just something extra you might think i will find usefull.<br><br>thank you so much for your help that i hope is coming! thanks!<br><br>25 ranger<br>uandar swiftarrow<br><br>9 shaman<br>faluddar <br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Sun Jan 27 08:53:55 2002</em><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
